data.text: Additions to my @SINow odds: US women gymnast survivors (9/1), Shaquem Griffin (20/1), Justify (triple crown-winning horse; 40/1).
@rmucatel @SInow Do you have a time machine to go back to 2008? If so, he’s still not winning, but he’s in the mix (also, maybe go back to the Ford Theater and save Lincoln first).

To be noted: these are my own just-for-fun personal odds. I do think for the sake of newsstand sales, @SInow might go with City of Philadelphia. I’ll give a final numbers after SEC championship, see if Tua moves up.
